### OTP Backend API Test Suite (current schema + rules)
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension
### Run top-to-bottom for a full flow.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7700

@creatorUsername = creator_api_test
@creatorEmail = creator_api_test@example.com
@creatorPassword = pass123

@user2Username = user2_api_test
@user2Email = user2_api_test@example.com
@user2Password = pass123

@user3Username = user3_api_test
@user3Email = user3_api_test@example.com
@user3Password = pass123

